OL,3,CKhan defends plans to shut police
OL,4,Cstation counters, despite election
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FSir Sadiq Khan has defended plans to
OL,8,Fshut police station front counters
OL,9,Facross London, despite an election
OL,10,Fpromise he made last year.
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police Service wants
OL,13,Fto cut the number of police stations
OL,14,Fopen to the public 24 hours a day in a
OL,15,Fbid to save money.
OL,17,FThe force is facing what it called
OL,18,F"tough choices" after government
OL,19,Fspending plans left it a #260m budget
OL,20,Fshortfall.
