OL,4,Cstation counters, despite election
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FThere are 32 police stations open 24/7
OL,8,F- one in each London borough.
OL,10,FBut the proposals would see just eight
OL,11,Ffront counters staffed around the
OL,12,Fclock - one for every three boroughs.
OL,14,FEleven of the 32 stations would switch
OL,15,Fto reduced opening hours but 13 would
OL,16,Fshut their front counters.
