OL,3,CKhan defends plans to shut police
OL,4,Cstation counters, despite election
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FSir Sadiq pledged in his 2024 election
OL,8,Fmanifesto: "I'll continue to ensure
OL,9,Fthe Met is able to effectively respond
OL,10,Fto the public, including maintaining a
OL,11,F24-hour police front office counter in
OL,12,Fevery borough."
OL,14,FBut today he told ITV News: "The
OL,15,Fcommission's got three criteria when
OL,16,Fit comes to front counters -
OL,17,Fresources, funding, and the demand of
OL,18,Fthe front counts.
