OL,3,CKhan defends plans to shut police
OL,4,Cstation counters, despite election
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,F"Some front counters will stay open 24
OL,8,Fhours a day in some boroughs in London
OL,9,Fwhere there is a demand, resources and
OL,10,Ffunding.
OL,12,F"Some boroughs, frankly speaking,
OL,13,Fnobody uses the front counters after
OL,14,Foffice hours, they'll stay open during
OL,15,Foffice hours, but after office hours
OL,16,Fthere will be other ways."
OL,18,FThe Met said there was no decision yet
OL,19,Fon which police stations will lose
OL,20,Ftheir front counters.
