OL,3,CKhan defends plans to shut police
OL,4,Cstation counters, despite election
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FA spokesperson said: "Just five per
OL,8,Fcent of crimes were reported using
OL,9,Ffront counters last year, with the
OL,10,Fvast majority of Londoners doing it
OL,11,Fover the phone, online, or in person
OL,12,Fwith officers elsewhere.
OL,14,F"Given the Met's budget shortfall and
OL,15,Fshrinking size, it is no longer
OL,16,Fsustainable to keep all front counters
OL,17,Fopen."
OL,19,FBut the proposed cuts were criticised
OL,20,Fby the Conservative rival Khan
OL,21,Fdefeated in the election.
